OL,3,CPensioners angry with changes to the
OL,4,Cwinter fuel allowance
OL,6,FITV Central's Lucy Kapasi spoke to
OL,7,Fpensioners feeling the squeeze
OL,9,FPensioners in Staffordshire are angry
OL,10,Fat the government's decision to scrap
OL,11,Fthe universal winter fuel allowance.
OL,13,FMP's have voted to cut the winter fuel
OL,14,Fallowance and now only the poorest
OL,15,Fpensioners will receive the benefit.
