OL,3,CPensioners angry with changes to the
OL,4,Cwinter fuel allowance
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fdefended the decision saying it was a
OL,8,F'choice we had to make' to help
OL,9,F'repair the public finances', despite
OL,10,Fwarnings that the cut could create 'a
OL,11,Fpublic health emergency'.
OL,13,FLast winter 10.8 million pensioners
OL,14,Freceived the Winter Fuel Payment. That
OL,15,Fnumber is expected to fall to 1.5
OL,16,Fmillion after the cut. It is estimated
OL,17,Fthe cut will save the government #1.3
OL,18,Fbillion.
