OL,3,CPensioners angry with changes to the
OL,4,Cwinter fuel allowance
OL,6,FThe government says the move is
OL,7,Fnecessary to help fill a #22 billion
OL,8,F"black hole" left by the Conservatives.
OL,10,FWhat is the Winter Fuel Payment?
OL,12,FThe Winter Fuel Payment is an annual,
OL,13,Ftax-free sum intended to give older
OL,14,Fpeople reassurance that they can
OL,15,Fafford to heat their homes in winter.
OL,16,FIt was paid to everyone who'd reached
OL,17,Fstate pension age.
