OL,3,CPensioners angry with changes to the
OL,4,Cwinter fuel allowance
OL,6,FThe payments were first introduced in
OL,7,F1997. The amounts have varied, but it
OL,8,Fis typically #200 - or #300 for
OL,9,Fhouseholds with someone over the age
OL,10,Fof 80.
OL,12,FMany also criticise the new system as
OL,13,Fover complicated. The Pensioners
OL,14,FConvention in North Staffordshire is
OL,15,Ftrying to combat that by training
OL,16,Fvolunteers to help those eligible
OL,17,Fclaim winter fuel allowance.
OL,19,FThey have also produced a leaflet to
OL,20,Fexplain whether you are able to claim
OL,21,Ffor the credit.
