OL,6,FThe Department of Work and Pensions
OL,7,Festimate that less than half those who
OL,8,Fqualify for pension credits claim for
OL,9,Fit. 880,000 pensions, out of the 1.5
OL,10,Fmillion entitled, don't claim any
OL,11,Fbenefit.
OL,13,FWho is eligible now?
OL,15,FThe winter fuel payment will be
OL,16,Flimited to only those over state
OL,17,Fpension age who claim pension credit
