OL,3,CPensioners angry with changes to the
OL,4,Cwinter fuel allowance
OL,6,FIf you are eligible, you'll normally
OL,7,Fget the winter fuel payment
OL,8,Fautomatically.
OL,10,FYou will get a letter in October or
OL,11,FNovember saying how much you'll get
OL,12,Fpaid.
OL,14,FIf you do not get a letter but you
OL,15,Fthink you're eligible, you can check
OL,16,Fon the government website if you need
OL,17,Fto make a claim. You might need to
OL,18,Fclaim if you live abroad, for example.
